  "body": "### New Features\r\n\r\n* Added zooming for the balance chart   https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/492\r\n* Added support for custom nLocktime   https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/481\r\n* Seamless update functionality on windows and easier updates on MacOS and Linux  https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/513\r\n* Bluetooth support for jade  https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/517\r\n* App lock mode  https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/519\r\n\r\n\r\n### Improvements\r\n\r\n* Notifications history now available from the tray icon  https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/493\r\n* bug fixes and small UI improvements\r\n\r\n### Contributions\r\n\r\n* @bsn21m made their first contribution in https://github.com/andreasgriffin/bitcoin-safe/pull/538\r\n* Thanks to the [bdk](https://github.com/bitcoindevkit/) team and @rustaceanrob \r\n* Huge thanks to @design-rrr for design and UX support\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Check out \r\n\r\n- www.bitcoin-safe.org\r\n- 🌍 Community forum: [chorus](https://chorus.community/group/34550%3Af8827954feef0092c8afec0be4cae544a9ed93dce9a365596e75b19aa05f0c84%3Abitcoin-safe-meiqbfki)\r\n- Follow on [nostr](https://yakihonne.com/profile/nprofile1qqsyz7tjgwuarktk88qvlnkzue3ja52c3e64s7pcdwj52egphdfll0cq9934g) or [X](https://x.com/BitcoinSafeOrg)\r\n\r\n####  Verify signature\r\n\r\nImport my [public key](https://keys.openpgp.org/vks/v1/by-fingerprint/2759AA7148568ECCB03B76301D82124B440F612D) and verify the signature with:\r\n```bash\r\ngpg --import 2759AA7148568ECCB03B76301D82124B440F612D.asc\r\ngpg --verify Bitcoin-Safe-1.8.0-x86_64.AppImage.asc\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
